rComments: Very unorganized. The assignments, tests and lectures were all very unorganized and poorly put together. Would try to avoid this professor.

2019 Winter was Prof. first semester teaching at York and she is amazing. She tried changing a few aspects of the course that is being taught the same way for ages. She added a group-project and gives mock-up lab test, midterm and exam. All in all, she is very thoughtful and tries to prepare you for the industry. Hope to take more courses with her.
